== 4.0.0 / 02-02-16
* changed syntax of connection, this is a breaking change.  Now options can be passed, so more than just the schema repo url can be set.
== 3.0.0 / 10-05-15
* changed "send" to "queue", to disambiguate it from the existing ruby "send" method.  This obviously breaks method calls to produce messages.
== 2.0.0 / 09-29-15
* pass broker url vs host/port to allow for multiple hosts and compatibility with other kafka stuff.  This breaks the new method from the old way.
== 1.0.4 / 09-28-15
* changed get_partition_ids to get only partitions with a leader
== 1.0.3 / 09-15-15
* added debug for serializer
== 1.0.2 / 09-04-15
* added avro serializer
== 1.0.1 / 08-17-15
* added round-robin and specific partition sends
== 1.0.0 / 08-10-15
* Initial release
